## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not cover all possible reasons for the failure of CoEs. The effectiveness of a CoE can vary significantly depending on the specific context and industry, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases based on their perspectives and experiences.